title.narrative: EARLY LEARNING

description.narrative: More young children have access to quality early learning opportunities, particularly in target countries., which contributes to Access To Quality Learning Opportunities, Early Childhood Development, Equitable Access To Quality Education, Health And Development In Early Childhood And Adolescence, Learning Outcomes, Learning, Skills, Participation And Engagement. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building, Systems Strengthening To Leave No One Behind. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: By 2022, more pre-primary, primary and lower secondary school aged and school-aged children particularly the most vulnerable, are in school and learning.
